default1.1 
defaultIn this submission to the Committee' Inquiry, I want to focus on specific points that have come out of several visits I have arranged, for politicians and others, looking at the different approach to Green Finance in Germany. There are other examples of more innovative approaches in North America, but I will focus on what other EU Member States are already doing within the single European market.
