default6.7 
defaultA wider financial and policy remit given to the Green Investment Bankdefault, 
defaulta more authoritative lead from governmentdefault (in setting higher standards of energy performance, in direct procurement of additional inter-connectors, and in driving 'community ownership' models of Green investment) and 
defaulta simpler, unified system of access to low-cost financedefault are all needed to deliver a coherent framework of Green Finance in the UK.
